data.text:
"Brainstem" is a song from Episode 3: Tokyo Grows/That Smarts/Brainstem. The song has Pinky and Brain (mostly Brain) sing about the parts of the human brain, to the tune of "Camptown Races".

Lyrics[]

And now, the parts of the brain, performed by The Brain!

Yes!

Neo-cortex, frontal lobe

Brainstem! Brainstem!

Hippocampus, neural node

Right hemisphere.

Pons and cortex visual

Brainstem! Brainstem!

Sylvian fissure, pineal

Left hemisphere.

Cerebellum left!

Cerebellum right!

Synapse, hypothalamus

Striatum, dendrite.

Axon fibers, matter gray

Brainstem! Brainstem!

Central tegmental pathway

Temporal lobe

White core matter, forebrain, skull

Brainstem! Brainstem!

Central fissure, cord spinal

Parietal.

Pia mater!

Menengeal vein!

Medulla oblongata and lobe limbic

Micro-electrodes...

Naaarf!

THE BRAIN!!!

That ought to keep the little squirts happy. Yes
